314320054.Title: Galanz 24 in. W 12 cu. ft. Frost Free Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel with Ice Maker, Silver

311302753.Title: ECO APPLICANCES INC 10.5 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless, Silver
311302753.Description: Seeking the ultimate addition to your energy-saving kitchen. Look no further than our 10.5 cu. ft. Top Mount Apartment Refrigerator in Stainless. 205951247.Title: Summit Appliance 10.3 cu. ft. Top Freezer Refrigerator in Stainless Steel, Counter Depth, Stainless Steel/Black
205951247.Description: The FF1159SSIM makes the ideal addition to any household kitchen looking for full storage capacity in a hard-to-find fit. At just 24" wide and under 60" high, the FF1159SSIM is perfectly sized for any location, including those complying with ADA guidelines for accessibility. This unit features reversible stainless steel doors and a textured black cabinet. Color: Stainless Steel/Black.
